wiki.summary: "Streets" is a song by American singer and rapper Doja Cat for her second album "Hot Pink". It was released on November 7, 2019, alongside the album, and later became a sleeper hit in January 2021. The song is produced by brother production-duo Blaq Tuxedo, who are also credited as co-writers. It gained its namesake from the song which is sampled throughout the track, "Streets Is Callin", by B2K from their soundtrack album "You Got Served". Read more on Last.fm.
